      "review_summary": "The PR adds a best-effort `reader.releaseLock()` after canceling the cloned reader used to classify missing-content-type OpenAI SDK stream bodies in `src/agents/provider-transport-fetch.ts`.\n\nPR surface: Source +3. Total +3 across 1 file.\n\nReproducibility: no. high-confidence full OpenClaw runtime reproduction is present. Source inspection plus a Node Web Streams probe show the current classifier cancels the cloned reader without releasing the lock.",
